fields.title: adidas Originals Yeezy Boost 350 v2 Shoe
fields.description:
The legendary adidas x Kanye West collaboration is supremely comfortable and has an edgy street style that will turn heads. The formfitting Primeknit upper is unlined and breathable, while the Clarino lining enhances performance longevity and prevents slip. Iconic adidas Boost midsole cushioning is ultra light and ultra responsive. Rubber outsole offers durability.

Formfitting Primeknit upper is unlined and breathable.
Clarino lining to prevent slip.
Premium suede arch support.
Antimicrobial sockliner cover.
Full-length internal Boost midsole cushioning is ultra light and ultra responsive.
Rubber outsole.

fields.title: Gucci Technical jersey sweatshirt
fields.description:
The sweatshirt continues to be a silhouette favored by Creative Director Alessandro Michele. The sportswear inspired style is made from a technical jersey fabric and trimmed with Gucci jacquard stripe along the sleeves. The sleeves can be removed using snaps along the shoulder seams, transitioning it to a sleeveless silhouette.

Black technical jersey
Gucci jacquard trim
Fixed hood
Snaps at the shoulder seams to remove sleeves
55% polyester and 45% cotton
Made in Italy
The model is 6’1” and is wearing size medium
